{"tid":2132125,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"很多事情的意義，往往是事後才知道，例如：最後一次選舉。","createTime":"2020-07-30T08:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T08:37:03.000Z","uid":97944,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be050e4e9f01c23b2d2861f1d96a9503ca1e5f30","tid":2132125,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/116310826_1221196448215121_7892490342311379544_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=EPaELz3sBlcAX_8yznS&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=9b607a9dc98afdf13cff12fcf633aa7e&amp;oe=5F4624B7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F116310826_1221196448215121_7892490342311379544_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DEPaELz3sBlcAX_8yznS%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D9b607a9dc98afdf13cff12fcf633aa7e%26oe%3D5F4624B7&h=24e5c90d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多事情的意義，往往是事後才知道，例如：最後一次選舉。<br />\n<br />\n圖為1932年7月31日德國國會大選，施萊謝爾將軍（General Kurt von Schleicher）投票後步出聯邦選舉票站。<br />\n<br />\n這是1933年納粹黨掌權之前，德國最後一次自由和公正的選舉，下一次已是1990年。<br />\n<br />\n選舉後，施萊謝爾短暫接任總理，兩個月後旋即被希特拉接任。<br />\n<br />\n1933年國會大選後，希特拉透過街頭威脅及政治恐嚇，迫令國會通過《授權法》，授予內閣無上權力，任意立法，德國越益趨向獨裁。<br />\n<br />\n1934年長刀之夜，施萊謝爾與妻子在別墅被納粹黨人槍殺。<br />\n<br />\nSource: Watershed Hong Kong<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WatershedHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWatershedHK%2F&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSqkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=0ea54ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WatershedHK/</a>"},{"pid":"e29163394765b7a0a189822bf2fad70b5d8fe542","tid":2132125,"uid":97944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:37:03.000Z","msg":"大家走得就走啦<br />\n再玩選舉已經無意思"}]}